\id MIC - Kuna, San Blas - Bible -Panama 2014 (DBL -2014)
\h Miqueas
\toc1 Miqueas-Garda
\toc2 Miqueas
\toc3 Mi
\mt1 MIQUEAS-GARDA
\mt2 MIQUEAS
\imt2 GEBE-SOGLENAID
\imt1 Garda-nug
\ip \it Miqueas-Garda.\it* Miqueasʼde Moresetʼginedid. Miqueasʼgi binsaleged we-dulede, Amósʼyobi sapurgi arbadii gusmoye. \it Doa Bab-Jehováʼyobidye,\it* Miqueas-nug obarileged.
\is1 Miqueas-Gardagi weyob sunmaklenaid
\ip Miqueas, Rey-Jotam-ibagangi, Rey-Acaz-ibagangi, degi, Rey-Ezequías-ibagangi gudii gusad.
\ip Miqueas, Judá-neggweburgi Bab-gayaburbagi sunmakdii gusad. Degi, Israel-neggweburgi sunmakdii gusbalid. Miqueas, sogdii gusad, yoedsega David-e-neguyagine, Rey-Dummadi gwalulenonikoye. We-Mesías, Belén-Efrata-neggweburgi gwalulenonikoye. We-gaya-sunmaksadi, Jesús-gwalulenonikoedgi sunmaksad. (Mateo 2:6)
\ip We-gardagine, weyob ilemakar sunmaklenaid:
\io1 1. Bab-Dummad Israel-dulemarga, degi, Judá-dulemarga igar-nabosad (1:1–3:12).
\io1 2. Bab-Jehová bela napneg semaid (4:1–5:15).
\io1 3. Israel-dulemar-isgusad, degi, Bab-Dummad Israel-dulemar-wiledaksad (6:1–7:20).
\ip Be itogua.
\c 1
\ms1 1. BAB-DUMMAD ISRAEL-DULEMARGA, DEGI, JUDÁ-DULEMARGA IGAR-NABOSAD
\mr (1:1–3:12)
\s1 Samariaʼga, degi, Jerusalénʼga naibi-itosad
\p 
\v 1 Judá-dule-e-reymar Jotam, Acaz, degi, Ezequías, negsemamaid-ibagangine, Bab-Jehová dule-Moreset-neggweburgined-Miqueasʼye-nugadga sunmaksad. Miqueas, Samaria-yalagi-negguoed, degi, Jerusalén-yalagi-negguoed weyob negburgan daksad.
\s1 Bab-Jehová-danikoed
\p Miqueas, Bab-Jehová-ega-sogsadba weyob sogded:
\q1 
\v 2 “Dulemar, bela we-yalagi-bukmalad be an-itomar,
\q2 bela napneggi-bukmalad, nue-bogimakar be itomalo.
\q1 Bab-Dummad-Jehová-Bela-Gangued-Nika-Maid, ese-goled-neg-akale, bemargi-gwisguega sunmakoed.
\q2 
\v 3 ¡Dakmala! Bab-Jehová, e-maidgi bato noalid, bato aidealid,
\q2 yar-mullugan-imbaba gannamakdanikid.
\q1 
\v 4 E-nanaedbali yarmar abin maludoed.
\q2 Ibmar-gwallu-soo-abin-daluddaedyobi yar gudoed,
\q1 igi diwar-noedbali, nebagan negabar-argaddae,
\q2 deyobi, nebagan argadoed.
\q1 
\v 5 Bela we-ibmarmar Jacob-wagan-Bab-Dummadgi-gwisgusadbali guoed.
\q2 Israel-dulemar-isgued-ular, deyob, guoed.
\q1 ¿Ar bia Jacob-wagan Bab-Dummadgi gwisgusmala?
\q2 ¿Ar Samaria-neggweburgi isgusmarsursi?
\q1 ¿Ar Jerusalén-neggweburgi, Judá-dulemar e-bab-dummaganse-gorleged-neggi isgusmarsursi?
\q2 
\v 6 A-ulale, Bab-Jehová soged:
\q1 ‘An Samaria-neggwebur akwamarbi dunnumaksii an imakoed.
\q2 E-akwamar nebaganba an mioed,
\q1 bela swanga an imakoed.
\q2 Unnila e-yala uvaʼmar-digega guoed.
\q1 
\v 7 Bela e-bab-dummadyob-imaklemalad bibislegoed.
\q2 Bela bab-dummagan-neggi-gambasamaladga ibmar-uklesmalad, ogumaklegoed.
\q1 Bela we-ibmarmar-soblesmalad an obelogoed.
\q2 Ar ade, galagwensuli-nanamalad-manigi, we-ibmarmar-soblesadi, gannar amar-maniga an imakoed.’ ”
\s1 Miqueas, Israel-dulemar-ular, bukib-itosad
\p 
\v 8 Miqueas sogded:
\q1 “Agala, an booed,
\q2 bukib-binsaedba an binnasuli goloed,
\q1 nag-swili an gudii guoed,
\q2 uka-swili an gudii guoed.
\q1 Achu-boeyobi an gordii guoed.
\q2 Irmonyobi an akigindii guoed.
\q1 
\v 9 Ar ade, Samaria-e-naibigusadi, gege nudakleged.
\q2 E-naibigusadi, bela Judá-yalase warmaksad.
\q2 Bela Jerusalén-neggweburse an-dulemar-bukwadse nasgusad.
\q1 
\v 10 Melle be bomalo,
\q2 melle Gat-neggweburgi be ibmar sogmalo.
\q1 Napayala nunmakedba, Bet-Le-Afra-neg-ukubgi be bindumakmar.
\q2 
\v 11 Safirʼginmalad, uka-swiri binged-abalagi be-yargi be nomar.
\q1 Zaanánʼginmaladdi, ainiega sikirmaksamalad.
\q2 Betesel-neggweburgi ogormakdemalad, bar bemar bendaklegosulid.
\q1 
\v 12 Marotʼginmalad, ibmar-nued-gued abebukwad,
\q2 ar Bab-Jehováʼdi, Jerusalén-neggwebur-dogedse bonigan barmialid.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 ”Laquis-dorgan, bemar ur-bila-onomaladgi moli be nasikmar.
\q2 Ar ade, be-neggwebur-Jerusalénʼgi isgued noalid,
\q2 bemargine, Israel-dulemar-e-isgued noalid.
\q1 
\v 14 Degisoggu, Moreset-Gat-neggweburga degimaloye be sogmalo.
\q2 Aczib-neggwebur-e-negmar, Israel-dulemar-e-reymar-yardakega gued.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 ”Maresa-dorgan, dule-wargwen be-ibe-yarsuega, an bemargi barmidoed.
\q2 Adulam-akwasaila-yaa-ollogwadyaba Israel-dule-bulegan dukunamaloed.
\q1 
\v 16 Degisoggu, be-mimmigan-sabed-ulale, be bukib-binsae,
\q2 aku-siga be esie,
\q1 mula-nono-swirigwadyobi be-nono swiri be imake,
\q2 ar ade, be-mimmigan yogasaar-gales dikasuli begi seledmaloed.”
\c 2
\s1 Dule, dule-wileged-mesagwar-imakdiid, duledar-wiles
\q1 
\v 1 Dule, igar-isgana-imakedgi-binsamalad, duledar-wilesmar.
\q2 Ar megidele, igar-isgana-imakedgi, binsamaidamalad.
\q1 Neg-oibosale, igar-isgana imakdedamalad,
\q2 ar ade, e-ibmar-imakbiedba imakdamalad.
\q1 
\v 2 We-dulemar, emar-nainubina sokalile, e-ibe susdamalad, egadga imakdedamalad.
\q2 Emar-ibe negmar susdamalad, egadga imakdedamalad.
\q1 E-neg-ibed-mesagwar imakdedamalad,
\q2 degi, e-neg-ibed-mimmigan-mesagwar imakdedamarbalid.
\q1 E-nainu-ibed-mesagwar imakdedamalad,
\q2 degi, e-nainu e-ibe susdamarbalid.
\p 
\v 3 Degisoggu, Bab-Jehová weyob soged:
\q1 “Emigine, ani, an we-dulemar-isganagi bonigan barmidamogoed,
\q2 we-bonigangi gwen wakinnosurmalad.
\q1 Bar san-dummarbaa na itogosurmalad,
\q2 ar ade, e-sabsur-odurdakleged-wachimar omosad.
\q1 
\v 4 A-ibagan-omosale, dule-bamalad egi dododmaloed,
\q2 ega we-naibi-itoleged-namakleged weyob egi dodoar namakmaloed:
\q1 ‘Anmar bela bergusmala.
\q2 An-dulamar-ibe nainumar miminanaid,
\q1 ibiyobi anmar-ibe nainumar sunanai.
\q2 Dule-isganamar, anmar-nainumar miminanaid.’ ”
\b
\q1 
\v 5 A-ulale, Bab-Jehová-sordagan-onmakbukwad-abargi,
\q2 we-dulemarga napa-mimilegedgi ega napa uklegosulid.
\s1 Bab-Dummad-gayaburba-barsoged-napiragwadsurmalad
\p 
\v 6 We-gayaburba-barsoged-napiragwadsurmalad anga soged:
\q1 “Mer bar be anmarga ee-gordii samala.
\q2 Mer be anmarga soge, be wilemaloye.”
\q1 
\v 7 Jacob-wagan weyob sogmalad:
\q1 “¿Bab-Jehová e-san-bargaagwar-imaked bergussi? E-daedde, ¿weyobsi?
\q2 ¿Ar dule-inniki-nanadiidga Bab-Dummad-gayaburba ibnuedga gusursi?”
\q1 
\v 8 Bab-Jehová soged: “Ar bemar an-dulamarga gumalanad,
\q2 degi-inigwele, emi-ibagi be an-isdarmaladga gudmalad.
\q1 Dulemar-igarba-baisurbinsa-nadapdamalad-ibe sordamar-be-isdarmaladyobi, e-ibe be mor-nuegan atursasdamalad.
\q2 
\v 9 An-dulamar-omegan e-neg-nuegangi be ononnosmalad.
\q2 A-omegan-e-mimmigan-ibe, be e-wergued osulosmalad.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 ”¡Ogusmar! ¡Be namar!
\q2 We-nega, obunnoged-negsulid.
\q1 Bela nue-isgus naid,
\q2 bela oitoles siid.
\q1 
\v 11 Ar dule-gwensak yogasaar-gakansaedgi
\q1 weyob sognonikile:
\q2 ‘An bemarga-sunmakega, vino be anga udamaloye,
\q2 sisa be anga udamaloye.’
\q1 We-neggwebur Bab-Dummad-gayaburba-barsogedyobi, we-dule-dakdoed.”
\s1 Gales-bukwadgi onolemaloye soglesad
\p 
\v 12 Bab-Jehová sogdebalid:
\q1 “Jacob-wagan, an bemarga nue-napira-soged,
\q2 bela be-dulemar gannar nuekwa an urboed.
\q1 Israel-wagan, an bemarga nue-napira-soged,
\q2 bemar-napi-besmaladi, an gannar danar urboed.
\q1 Igi sibad-wawaad galu-yaba danale-bukwadae,
\q2 deyobi, an bemar-urboed.
\q1 Degi, igi sibad-wawaad gagan-araramaladgi bukwadae,
\q2 deyobi, an bemar-urboed,
\q2 degine, binnasuli dule-bukidarayob oimakdemaloed.”\fig Sibad-wawaad-edarbed galu-yaba sibad-wawaad-urbisad. (Miqueas 2:12) |src="LB00014B.TIF" size="col" ref="Miqueas 2:12"\fig*
\q1 
\v 13 Ega igar-mayedi, emar-idumai guoed,
\q2 deginbali, emarmoga, igar-egamai gumarmogoed.
\q1 Amar, igar-bulegangi ollorgumaloed, degi, namaloed.
\q2 E-reydi, amar-idumai guoed.
\q2 Bab-Jehová, na e-sunnagwadi emar-idumai guoed.
\c 3
\s1 Dule-negsemamaid-isganamar sabsur-odurdaklegoed
\p 
\v 1 Geb degine, an sogded:
\q1 “Jacob-dulemar-negsemamaid, Israel-dulemar-e-dummagan, nue be an-itomar:
\q2 Bemar bur igar-innikigwad-imaked-durdaked ¿nabirsursi?
\q1 
\v 2 Ar bemar igar-nued bur isdar dakmalad,
\q2 igar-isgana aka be yeer dakmalad.
\q1 An-dulamar be wiodimalad,
\q2 mesagwar be imakdimalad.
\q1 
\v 3 Bemar ibgwensur an-dulamar imakdimalad.
\q2 E-ukamar e-ibe be edared.
\q2 E-garmar bis-bis e-ibe be imaked.
\q1 Igi san-olomakar esmed-yagi onakledae, deyobi, an-dulamar be wiodimalad.
\q2 San-narilegedyobi, an-dulamar be imakdimalad.”
\b
\q1 
\v 4 Bemar ibagwengi Bab-Jehováʼse gotemaloed,
\q2 edina, bemar-abin imakosulid.
\q1 Ar bemar dogdar isgusgudiidba,
\q2 a-ibagangine, bemar-idu banguoed.
\s1 Bab-Dummad-gayaburba-barsogmalad
\p 
\v 5 Bab-Jehová weyob bemar-annik soged:
\q1 “Bemar Bab-gayaburba-barsogmalad,
\q2 dulemar-yamodimalad, igar-noaledba an-dulamar-sedimalad:
\q1 Unnila dule-bega-masgunned-ukmaladgarbi, igar-bogidikidgi be sunmakdamalad,
\q2 ar dule-bega-masgunned-uksurmaladgardi, bila-onoged be obariddamalad.
\q1 
\v 6 Degisoggu, an bar bemarga an-ibmar-sabiedi sogosulid.
\q2 Bipisaale bar an bemarga an-gayaburba sogosulid.
\q1 Bar anga-gayaburba-barsogmalad bemarga yoedse-ibmar-guoedgi sunmakosurmalad.
\b
\q1 ”An-gayaburba-barsogmalad bar sunmaksuli guoed
\q2 e-ibagan bergudoed.
\q1 
\v 7 An-gayaburba-barsogmaladi, bingedar itodmaloed.
\q2 Nergan aku neg-dake gudmaloed.
\q1 Ar bela wemar bar-ibmar sogosurmalad,
\q2 ar ade, an gwen ega ibmar sogosulid.”
\q1 
\v 8 Andi, Miqueas, Bab-Jehová-Burba nue-nika gudiid.
\q2 Igar-napiragwadi, degi, garganguedi, an nue-nika gudiid.
\q1 Adi, Jacob-dulemar ibmar-isgana-imakmaladgi an sunmakegar,
\q2 degi, Israel-dulemar-isgudiidgi an sunmakegar.
\s1 Jerusalén-neggwebur oitolesad
\q1 
\v 9 Jacob-dulemar-negsemamaid, Israel-dulemar-e-dummagan, be nue an-itomalo.
\q2 Bemar igar-innikimalad bur be obandimalad.
\q2 Bipisaale, bemar igar-maidgi binsaed-nika dasurmalad.
\q1 
\v 10 Ablis-eogedgi Sión-neggwebur be sobsamalad
\q2 igar-isgana-imaklegedba be Jerusalén-neggwebur sebukmalad.
\q1 
\v 11 Be-dummagan-negsemaladi, dule-baiganse-manigi-baklegar igar nabomalad.
\q2 Be-dule-irwa-Bab-Jehováʼse-gormaladi, manigi-bennuklegar dule-odurdakmalad,
\q1 degi, be-Bab-Jehová-gayaburba-barsogmaladi, manigi-bennuklegar dulega sunmakmalad,
\q2 aka bur Bab-Jehováʼga weyob sogdedamalad:
\q1 “¿Ar Bab-Jehováʼde anmarba gudisursi?
\q2 Degisoggu, anmar akar-guosulid.”
\q1 
\v 12 A-ulale, bemar-nukine Sión-neggwebur nainu-imuar-naidaedyob guoed.
\q2 Jerusalén-neggwebur akwamarbi ganna-ganna-bubukwa guoed.
\q2 Bab-Jehováʼse-goled-neg-e-yala, gannar sapurbi moodo naguoed.
\c 4
\ms1 2. BAB-JEHOVÁ BELA NAPNEG SEMAID
\mr (4:1–5:15)
\s1 Sión-yala nug-dummarbaa guoed
\r (Isaías 2:1-5)
\q1 
\v 1 Ibagan-bergued-mosale, Bab-Jehováʼse-goled-neg-yala bur yala-biriginedga guoed,
\q2 yala-mulluganba bur nuga-nika guoed.
\q1 Dulemar-yar-baid-baidgi-bukmalad bela ase nonimaloed.
\q2 
\v 2 Dule-yar-baid-baidgi-bukmalad-bukidar-nonikoedi, sognonimaloed:
\q1 “Dagmar, anmar Bab-Jehová-yalase nakwenamar,
\q2 Jacob-e-Bab-Dummadse-goled-negse anmar namar.
\q1 Bab-Dummad, e-sunnad, e-igar-maidba anmar-odurdakoed,
\q2 degi, anmar e-igarba nanadii gumaloed.”
\q1 Ar ade, Sión-yalagi Bab-Dummad-Igar-Maid-odurdakleged danikid,
\q2 Jerusalén-neggweburgi Bab-Jehová-gayaburba ainidagoed.
\q1 
\v 3 Bab-Dummad, dulemar-yar-baid-baid-abargi dulemarga igar-nabogoed,
\q2 neggwebur-gandikmalad-bukibga, degi, dikasurmaladga igar-nabogega guoed.
\q1 E-es-suidmar napa-imuedga gudoed,
\q2 e-ila-swiswidikmalad es-dopegwadga gudoed.
\q1 Dule-yar-baid-baidginmalad, bar abin-abin urwosurmalad.
\q2 Bila-onogega, bar guagwar-gudii guosurmalad.
\q1 
\v 4 Bela dulemar bogidik e-uva-dubmar-urba-bukwa gumaloed,
\q2 degi, bogidik e-higuera-sapi-urba-bukwa gumaloed,
\q1 dule-bamaladi, gwen amar-ogwayosulid,
\q2 ar ade, deyobi, Bab-Jehová-Bela-Gangued-Nikad sogsad.
\q1 
\v 5 Ar bela dulemar e-bab-dummagan-nug ogannomalale, akarsulid,
\q2 ar anmardi, anmar-Bab-Dummad-Jehová-Bela-Gangued-Nikad-e-nugbi odummodii guoed.
\s1 Bab-Jehová, Israel-dulemar-gales-selesmalad onogoed
\p 
\v 6 Bab-Jehová weyob sogded:
\q1 “A-ibagangine, dulemar-nailikguarmalad nuekwa an urboed.
\q2 Dulemar-yar-baid-baidse-mimilesmalad bulakwaa an oambikuoed,
\q2 degi, sabsur-imakledimalad nuekwa an oambikuoed.
\q1 
\v 7 Dulemar-nailikguarmalad napi besmaloed.
\q2 Amarde, neggweburga an imakoed.
\q1 Dulemar-yar-baid-baidse-mimilesmaladgi,
\q2 dulamar-bela-bela-gangued-nikadga an imakoed.
\q1 Ani Bab-Jehová ega Sión-yalagi yar-seoed,
\q2 degisadegu yar-semai guoed.
\q1 
\v 8 Sión-yala, Jerusalén-neggweburgi be siid,
\q2 neg-matusulid-nakulegedga be gunonikid.
\q1 Be epennegwadyobi, gannar gangued-nika be guoed,
\q2 Jerusalén, epenne be negsesadyobi, gannar be negseoed.”
\s1 Sión-yala sabsur-wilegoed, geb weligwar-itobaloed
\q1 
\v 9 Emide, Jerusalén, ¿ibiga be binnasuli gole?
\q2 ¿Ar be, rey satesi?
\q1 ¿Ibiga begi naibid-dummad noniki?
\q2 ¿Ar bega-binsaed-uked burgwissi?
\q1 
\v 10 Sión-dulemar, ome-ugakgunaidaedyob, be binnasuli gole,
\q2 be binnasuli akiginne.
\q1 Ar be-neggweburgi be nooed,
\q2 magabali gaamakdii be guoed.
\q1 Babilonia-yalase be naoed.
\q2 Geb agine, be ollorgunonikoed,
\q2 Bab-Jehová be-isdarmaladgine be-onogoed.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 Emigindi, dulemar-yar-baid-baidgi-bukwad-bukidar begi-gwisguega atosmalad.
\q2 Weyob sogmalad:
\q1 “Sión-yala-ibe anmar ibmar sunae.
\q2 ¡Bitigi, Sión-yala galakusa an daksamalana yeerbanye!”
\q1 
\v 12 Degi-inigwele, we-dulemar Bab-Jehová-e-binsanaidi, degi, e-ibmar-imakbiedi wissurmalad.
\q2 Ar wemar wissurmalad, Bab-Jehová oros-dugmaklegedyobi e-saboleged-neggi e-urbemaloed.
\q1 
\v 13 Bab-Jehová sogdebalid: “Sión-dulemar, ¡ogusmar!
\q2 Oros-omukueyob be dulemar imaknamar.
\q1 Ar ani an moli-bebe-esgorogi-sobaledyobi gargangued an bega ukoed.
\q2 Moli-e-nag-goonasi-esgoro-gordikidgi-sobaledyobi, an bega gargangued ukbaloed.
\q1 Adi, bukidar neggwebur-bamalad napabi-nai be imakegar,
\q2 degi, bela e-ibmar-nuegan be ei subaligar.
\q1 Geb agine, a-ibmarmar anga be ukoed.
\q2 Ani an Bab-Jehová Napneg-E-Dummadga gued.”
\c 5
\s1 Dule-emar-onoged negseoed
\q1 
\v 1 Jerusalén-dorgan, be-sorda-bila-onomalad guagwar be urbemar.
\q2 Ar ade, anmar-isdarmalad bela anmar-ebiris bukmalad.
\q1 Israel-dulemar-e-dummad-negsemaidi, sabsur-wiolegoed.
\q2 
\v 2 Bab-Jehová sogdebalid:
\q1 “Belén-Efrata, ar bedi Judá-yargi-neggweburmar-bukwadba bur bipigwadid.
\q2 Begine, dule-Israel-yala-seoed nodagoed.
\q2 We-dulede, amba yoo-napaneg-nague bato gudibinned.”
\q1 
\v 3 A-ulale, Bab-Dummad, omegwa-goe-baknonikoedse be-isdarmaladga be-urmakmaloed.
\q2 Geb degine, Israel-dulemar-yar-baid-baidgi-napi-besmaladi, Israel-dulemar-baiganbo bular bukunonikoed.
\q1 
\v 4 Geb a-dule Bab-Jehová-e-ganguedba,
\q2 e-Bab-Dummad-Jehová-e-nug-gandikidba, e-dulemar-idugoed.
\q1 Dulemar, dobedsuli gudii gumaloed,
\q2 ar ade, a-dule bela napaneg-naid seoed.
\q2 
\v 5 Ar a-dule neg-bogidikid senonikoed.
\q1 Ar Asiria-dulemar anmar-yar-subiguarmalale, anmar-neg-gandikmalad-bibisbiguarmalale, a-dule, anmar-bendaknonikoed.
\q2 E-abin e-gugle (7) dummagan barmidoed,
\q2 degi, e-baabak (8) neggwebur-sapin-dummagan barmidabaloed.
\q1 
\v 6 Wemala, gandikidba dadsaila-Nimrod-yala Asiriaʼye-nugad semai gumaloed,
\q2 Asiria-dulemar anmar-yar subiguarmalale, degi, anmar-yar-abingunanaidgi dogbiguarmalale, a-dule, anmar-bendakoed.
\s1 Israel-dulemar-napi-besmalad
\q1 
\v 7 Igi Bab-Jehová wakudaryala boo-bomiardae,
\q1 degi, igi gagangi dii-owiardabali,
\q2 debayobi, Jacob-wagan-napi-besmaladi, neggwebur-bamalad-abargine gudii gumaloed.
\q1 Gaganmar gwen dule-eoged abdakdasulid
\q2 deyobi, gumaloed.
\q1 
\v 8 Igi achumigur-nono-wawaad, ibdurgan-sapurbarmalad-imbagi gudidae,
\q2 debayobi, Jacob-wagan-napi-besmaladi gumaloed.
\q1 Igi achumigur-senigwad sibad-wawaad-bukwadgi-gudiidgi,
\q2 sibad-wawaad-gasadae,
\q1 gwen-odulodasuli,
\q2 debayobi, Jacob-wagan neggwebur-bamalad-imbagine gudigumaloed.
\q1 
\v 9 Bab-Jehová, bee be, be-isdarmaladgi gwichiguoed,
\q2 bela be-isdarmalad be obelogoed.
\s1 Bab-dummaganga-imaklemalad berguoed
\p 
\v 10 Bab-Jehová weyob Israel-dulemarga sogded:
\q1 “A-ibagangine, an be-molimar ogilogoed,
\q2 degi, be-moli-ur-bila-onomalad an obelogoed.
\q1 
\v 11 An bela be-neggweburmar obelogoed,
\q2 degi, be-neg-gandikmalad bela an obelogoed.
\q1 
\v 12 Bela dulemar ina-isgana-imakmalad an obelogoed,
\q2 degi, bar be nergan-nika guosurmalad.
\q1 
\v 13 An bela be-bab-dummadyob-imaklemalad obelogoed,
\q2 degi, akwa-dummagan-islidikmalad an bela obelobaloed.
\q1 Bipisaale, be-ibmar-sobsamalad-asabin bar sindigar be sigosurmalad.
\q2 
\v 14 Be-bab-bundor-Asera-e-wilub-gwismalad an bemar-ibe ungoed,
\q1 degi, bela be-neggweburmar an obelogoed.
\q2 
\v 15 Dule-yar-baid-baidgi-bukmalad an-sogedba-dasurmalad ise-urwedgi, degi, sae-itogedgine, an buged imakoed.”
\c 6
\ms1 3. ISRAEL-DULEMAR-ISGUSAD, DEGI, BAB-DUMMAD ISRAEL-DULEMAR-WILEDAKSAD
\mr (6:1–7:20)
\s1 Bab-Dummad Israel-dulemarse ulusad
\p 
\v 1 Israel-dulemar, Bab-Jehová-ibmar-sogedi be nue itomar:
\q1 “Be gwichigumar. Be boni-nikagudiid yarmar-asabin be sognamar.
\q2 Yar-mullugana be-itogega be imakmar.”
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Yalamar, Bab-Jehová-urwed be itomar,
\q2 napa-e-saila-gandikmalad, nue be bogimakar itomar,
\q1 Bab-Jehová, e-dulemarga igar itosokalid,
\q2 Israel-dulemargi gwisgusokalid.
\b
\q1 
\v 3 Bab-Jehová sogded: “An-dulamar, ¿igi an bemar-imaksa?
\q2 Be anga-sogmala, ¿ibigi an begi nosa?
\q1 
\v 4 Ar ani an Egipto-yalagi bemar-onosadid,
\q2 maigagudiid-yalagi an bemar-ollor-imaksadid.
\q1 Ani an bemarga Moisés, Aarón, María, barmisgusadid,
\q2 adi, amar bemar-idumalagar.
\q1 
\v 5 An-dulamar, be-ebinsamala,
\q2 Moab-dulemar-e-rey-Balac bemar-wiogega bemar-idu igar amisgusanad.
\q1 Beor-machi-Balaam, igi Balac-abin sogsagusa,
\q2 a be nue-ebinsamala.
\q1 Deginbali, Sitimʼye-neg-nugad-akale, Gilgal-neg-nugadse-be-nonigusmaladi, be ebinsabali.
\q2 Magar be an-dakmala,
\q2 ani an, Bab-Jehová bemar-onosadid.”
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Emide be sogmalad:
\q1 “Anmarde, ¿igi Bab-Jehová-walikaa gumalosunna?
\q2 ¿Igi anmar Bab-Dummad-Bur-Birigined-asabin sindigar sigmalosunna?
\q1 ¿Moli-bebe-nikad-birgagwenad-ogumakar-ukleged, an ega ukega sedoe?
\q2 
\v 7 An sibad-wawaad-machered miliba (1000) Bab-Jehováʼga uker, Bab-Jehová ¿yeer itogoe?
\q1 Olivo-gwallu bute-miliambe (10,000) an ega uker, ¿yeer itogoe?
\q2 An ibmar-isgana-imaksad-ular, ¿an-machi-sailagined an ukoe?
\q2 An-machi-sunnad, ¿an-isgued-ular, an ukoe?”
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Ar Bab-Jehová bato bega sogsad ibu ibmar-nuedi.
\q2 Bab-Jehová be-daed-abemaidi, bato bega sogsad:
\q1 Igar-napiragwad-imaked be-abemaid,
\q2 dule-wiledaked be-abemaid,
\q2 e-asabin gwage-eikwadaed be-abemaid.
\s1 Jerusalén-dulemar sabsur-odurdaklegoed
\q1 
\v 9 Jerusalén-dulemar, Bab-Jehová-ibmar-soged nue be itomar:
\q2 Dule Bab-Dummad-dobee-nanadiile,
\q2 a-dule, dule-binsaed-ibedid.
\q1 Sabsur-odurdaklenaid nue be itomala.
\q2 Bega dule-odurdakleged-barmialidi, nue be itomala.
\q1 
\v 10 “¡Dule-isganamar! Ande be-ibmar-nuegan ibmar-isgana-imakedba-amisad, ¿baisurdakode?
\q2 Degi, ande be ibmar-wilubsamalad-isgana, ¿baisurdakode? ¡Adi surbali!
\q1 
\v 11 Ar ande, dule ibmar-wilubsaed-nuegansulid-ebudiid ¿igi yeer dakosunna?
\q2 Degi, ibmar-wilubdaked-ebudiid, ¿an igi yeer dakosunna? ¡Geg an yeer daked!
\q1 
\v 12 Dule-mani-ibegan, sabsur dule-imakedid.
\q2 Bela neggweburginmalad, gakansilimalad.
\q2 Na e-ibmar-sogedi bela gakansaedbiid.
\q1 
\v 13 Emisgine, ani an sabsur-be-imakmaloed,
\q2 bemar-isgued-ular, an bemar-obelogoed.
\q1 
\v 14 Na be mas-gunmalo-inigwele, gwen be immelegosurmalad,
\q2 amba ukudmaada be gudii gumaloed.
\q1 Be ibmar-gwag weemaloe-inigwele, be-ibe berguoed.
\q2 Ar be ibmar-soggwensaar-gaoedi, ani an bila-onolegedgi be-ibe obelogoed.
\q1 
\v 15 Be ibmar-digmaloedi, gwen be weosurmalad,
\q2 degi, be olivo-gwallu-egurmaloedi, gwen be ebugosurmalad.
\q2 Vino-onogega uva-nis-egurusadi, be gobosurmarbalid.
\b
\q1 
\v 16 ”Rey-Omri-igar-mesisadba be nanadimalad,
\q2 bela Rey-Acab-e-wagan-ibmar-isgana-imaksadba be ibmar-imakdimalad.
\q1 Amar-ibmar-imaksadyobi be nanadiid.
\q2 A-ulale, an bemar-obeloged imakoed.
\q1 Be-dulemar bingedar-itogega an saoed.
\q2 Dulemar-begi-dodoedi, an imakoed.”
\c 7
\s1 Miqueas, dulemar-isgudiidga bukib-itoged
\p 
\v 1 Miqueas sogded:
\q1 “¡An duledar-wiles!
\q2 Ibmar-gwag-yorgi-weleged-abin an nonisulid.
\q2 Uva-solagan-weleged-abin an nonisulid.
\q1 Degisoggu, uva-san-dukgwenad bar an daksulid,
\q2 degi, an higuera-san-gunnegala gwen an daksurbalid.
\q1 
\v 2 Dule-wiledakmalad bela neggweburgi obelolesad, we-yargi dule-innikimalad bergusad.
\q2 Bela dule-oburgwedgi-binsadimaladi, na muchub-muchub yamodidimalad.
\q1 
\v 3 Ibmar-isgana-imakedgi dule gwen egi obinsulid.
\q2 Dule-dummagan-negsemamaid, degi, dule-igar-nabomalad, dule-bamaladse manigi-baklegar, igar nabomalad.
\q1 Dule-gandikmalad e-itolegedba ibmar egismalad,
\q2 e-ibmar-abegedba ega ukdamalad.
\q1 
\v 4 A-dulemar-abargi wis-dule-nuegan-gudimaladdina,
\q2 bur bule sapi-ikobiidyob gued.
\q1 A-dulemar-abargi dule-bur-innikigwaddina, bur bule ikomaryob gued.
\q2 Suli-suli-itoleged-e-ibadi begi danikid,
\q1 Bab-gayaburba-barsogmalad bega-ibmar-sogsadyobi, sabsur-odurdakleged-iba bato bega warmaksad.
\q2 
\v 5 Degisoggu, melle be-ai-ibmar-soged be itogo,
\q1 degi, melle dule-baid-bega-ibmar-soged be itogo.
\q2 Be-ome-ebo be sunmakalile, nue-itoakwaa be sunmako.
\q1 
\v 6 Ar ade, masmala, e-sergangi binsaedsuli guded,
\q2 bunamala, nangangi obited,
\q1 balamar, sak-omegangi obited,
\q2 degi, e-isdarmaladi, e-neguyaginmalad nanaed.
\q1 
\v 7 Degi-inigwele, ani Miqueas, Bab-Jehováʼgi an bensulid,
\q2 Bab-Dummad-an-abonogedi, an edarbedii guoed.
\q2 An-Bab-Dummadi, an-itogoed.”
\s1 Israel-dulemar bendaklegoed
\p 
\v 8 Miqueas weyob sogded:
\q1 “An-isdarmalad-yar-baid-baidgi-bukmalad, mer be an-odurdaklegedgi weligwar itomala.
\q2 Ar an galakus-inigwele, amba an gannar gwisguoed.
\q1 An negsichidgi gudii-inigwele, ar Bab-Jehová neg-meegwadga anga gued.
\q2 
\v 9 Ar Bab-Jehováʼgi an isgusad,
\q1 degisoggu, Bab-Dummad-anga-igar-nudakedse,
\q2 degi, anga-igar-nabogedse an e-urwed itogoed.
\q1 Geb Bab-Jehová, igar-nued anga oyogoed,
\q2 degi, e-an-abonosadgi an werguoed.
\q1 
\v 10 An-isdarad anga sokardaed: ‘¿Bia be-Bab-Jehováʼde?
\q2 A-dule, an-dakalile, bingedar itodoed.’
\q1 An-sunnagwad an-ibya-nuki e-wilegoed an dakoed.
\q2 A-dule, neg-imbaba-olligi-annalegedyobi guoed.
\b
\q1 
\v 11 ”Jerusalén, gannar be-galu-matusurmalad-sobledele,
\q2 be-yar-abingunanaid nasgudoed.
\q1 
\v 12 A-ibagangine, dule-bamalad, Asiria-yala-akale, Egipto-yalase-dulemar-bukwad, bese nonimaloed.
\q2 Nilo-diwar-akale, Éufrates-diwarse-dulemar-bukwad, bese nonimaloed.
\q1 Demarsik-bukmalad-akale, demar-baidsik-bukmaladse-dulemar-bukwad, bese nonimaloed.
\q2 Deginbali, yar-dummagansik-bukmalad-akale, yar-dummagan-baidsik-bukmaladse-dulemar-bukwad, bela bese nonimaloed.
\q1 
\v 13 Dule-isgusmalad-ular, we-napneg olloo naguoed,
\q2 deyobi, neg naguoed.”
\s1 Bab-Jehová, Israel-dulemar-wiledakoed
\q1 
\v 14 Bab-Jehová, be-dulamar be nue ako,
\q2 be-mimmigan walagwengi sapur-nuedgi-bukmalad be nue akwedii be guo.
\q1 Epennegwadyobi be Basán-yalase, degi, Galaad-yalase be sede.
\q2 
\v 15 Egipto-yalagi Israel-dulemar-onosgu, ibmar-dakledisurmalad-oyosayobi, be oyoge.
\q1 
\v 16 Dulemar-yar-baid-baidgi-bukmaladi, be-ibmar-gegerdaklemalad dakmaloed.
\q2 Be-gandikid-dakoedba bingedar itodmaloed,
\q1 geger-dakedba gaya-gadmaloed,
\q2 degi, uaya-atidmaloed.
\q1 
\v 17 Igi-naibe napagi yaarmakar-nanae, deyobi, nanamaloed.
\q2 Ibdula-unimalad-unimakedyob gumaloed.
\q1 E-dukued-neggi dobed-abalagi nodamaloed,
\q2 be-asabin dobedgi ainidamaloed.
\q1 Anmar-Bab-Dummad-Jehová, bese, gannar we-dulemar nonimaloed.
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Bab-Dummad, ¿ar doa beyobid e-mimmigan-besmaladga isgusad-elied gudii?
\q2 ¿Doa beyobid ibmar-isgana-imaksad bela ei-ieged gudii?
\q1 Ar be degisadegu, urwedii guosulid,
\q2 ar ade, bur bule anmar-sabguedgi be binsaed.
\q1 
\v 19 Gannar wile be anmar-dake.
\q2 Anmar-isgued be osuloge,
\q2 anmar-isguedgi mer bar be binsae.
\q1 
\v 20 Jacob-waganga, be-ibmar-inniki-imaked, be oyoge,
\q2 Abraham-waganga, dule-ise-wiledaked be oyoge.
\q1 Epennegwa anmar-dadganga ise-sogar-imaksayobi, be ibmar imake.
